Package de.joemiagroup.krawumm

Class RegisteredUser

java.lang.Object
de.joemiagroup.krawumm.RegisteredUser
Record Components:
username - is the username of the user, has to be unique
email - is the email of the user, has to be unique
password - is the password of the user
isCreator - is true if the user uploaded an experiment in the past
uploadedExperiments - contains the experiments which the user uploaded, is empty if he never uploaded an experiment
bookmarks - contains the bookmarks of the user (Experiments)
loggedIn - is true if the user is logged in
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin
public class RegisteredUser
extends java.lang.Object
This class describes the registered user with all of their attributes (with setter and getter) and user specific functions: sendForm, rate, comment, searchComment, deleteComment, logOut, deleteAccount, changePassword, addFromBookmarks, deleteFromBookmarks
Author:
Jessica Eckardtsberg

    • sendForm

      public void sendForm​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String[] material, java.lang.String description, java.lang.String[] pictures, int indoorOutdoor, int age, float duration, int difficulty, java.lang.String video, java.lang.String[] instruction, RegisteredUser creator)
      This method puts a form into the main.formsList which means, that a user created a new experiment
      Parameters:
      name - is the name of the experiment
      material - is an array which contains the Materials needed for the experiments
      description - contains a short description text for the experiment (max 500 characters)
      pictures - contains pictures of the experiment
      indoorOutdoor - is 1 for indoor and 2 for outdoor
      age - holds the minimum age the child should be to do the experiment
      duration - holds the estimated time it takes to finish the experiment
      difficulty - holds a difficulty value between 1 and 5 (5 is hardest)
      video - contains vidoes of the experiment
      instruction - contains a instruction of the steps to do the experiment
      creator - holds a reference to the RegisteredUser who uploaded this experiment no return value
